&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The CM/ILS Program is seeking a qualified Logistician who brings experience in defense life-cycle logistics and configuration management for complex electronic and C4ISR systems. The ideal candidate will possess deep expertise in Integrated Logistics Support (ILS), product support strategy development, and sustainment planning, with a proven ability to analyze technical data, contracts, and system specifications to ensure effective and compliant logistics solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
